Will R. NOTTAGE, Appellant(s)/Petitioner(s),
v.
The STATE of Florida, Appellee(s)/Respondent(s), CASE NO.: 3D 17-1284 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Third District. SEPTEMBER 18, 2017 ROTHENBERG, C.J., and SALTER and LUCK, JJ., concur.

Following review of the State of Florida's motion to dismiss and appellant's response thereto, it is ordered that the above styled appeal is hereby dismissed as unauthorized.
